<span id="freeTextContainer10727187852763333301"><b>
  <i>&quot;Read it.<br/><br/>And if anyone asks you how it ends, just LIE.&quot;</i>
</b><br/><br/>This book was great,<br/> you guys! I love the writing style. <br/>It wasn&apos;t confusing at all! <br/>It was <i>totally</i> not annoying! :) <br/>I loved the characters.<br/>They were so complex<br/>and not bland at all.<br/>They definitely didn&apos;t <br/>want to make me want to shoot <br/>myself in the head! :)<br/>I knew what was going on and <br/>I enjoyed this story a lot! <br/>The ending was just beautiful. <br/>Literally all I can ask for! :)<br/><br/>I LOVE THIS SM I AM CRYING! :) :) :) :) :) :)</span>
  <span id="freeText10727187852763333301" style="display:none"><b>
  <i>"Read it.<br /><br />And if anyone asks you how it ends, just LIE."</i>
