<span id="freeTextContainer16198349186704714319">lets play two truths and a lie. ready? i will go first.<br/><br/> <blockquote> - this book has an unreliable narrator and you cant trust anything she tells you. <br/><br/> - this story has such deep secrets, even its secrets have secrets. <br/><br/> - this novel has a twist that you wont see coming, but you will try to convince yourself that you did. </blockquote><br/>think you got it?<br/><br/>i can guarantee you dont.<br/><br/>because the best lies are those based on truth.<br/><br/>so read this book for yourself.<br/><br/>maybe then you will be able to spot the imposter.<br/><br/>and if anyone asks y</span>
