        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer989018611" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12225456268906115584">THAT ENDING.<br/>I knew that the ending was going to be a huge twist and I kept trying to come up with different twists in my head while reading, but I didn&apos;t even come close to what it really was.<br/>I got a little annoyed with Cadence after a while of her complaining, but the character development was wonderful. I couldn&apos;t give it 5/5 because I didn&apos;t really find myself attached to any of the characters. Still recommend to anyone who would like to read a suspenseful contemporary book and, obviously, I </span>
  <span id="freeText12225456268906115584" style="display:none">THAT ENDING.<br />I knew that the ending was going to be a huge twist and I kept trying to come up with different twists in my head while reading, but I didn't even come close to what it really was.<br />I got a little annoyed with Cadence after a while of her complaining, but the character development was wonderful. I couldn't give it 5/5 because I didn't really find myself attached to any of the characters. Still recommend to anyone who would like to read a suspenseful contemporary book and, obviously, I suggest that you go into this book blindly. </span>
